# Review Checklist

A quick pass for PRs that touch Pathogen UI, styles, previews, or these docs.

## Does it fit?

- [ ] Visual choices help workflow, state, or hierarchy — not decoration?
- [ ] Matches [Foundations](<%= page_path :design-system-design-contract %>)
- [ ] Exception documented if you bent a rule?
- [ ] Local pattern worth promoting to Pathogen?
- [ ] Feels natural for the task?

## Colour and tokens

- [ ] `--pvc-color-*` where available?
- [ ] No new `slate-*` (use `neutral-*`)?
- [ ] Host can still override `--color-primary-*`?
- [ ] Status colour only for status?
- [ ] No hard-coded host brand in shared components?
- [ ] Big colour fields only for selection, focus, status, nav?
- [ ] Solid hover darkens, not lightens?
- [ ] Success/warning as text/border/icon only (no solid fill yet)?

## Type and spacing

- [ ] Mostly 14px / 16px unless hierarchy needs more?
- [ ] Labels semibold at control scale?
- [ ] 4px spacing scale, no odd gaps?
- [ ] Page titles via `Heading` component?

## Surfaces and radius

- [ ] Radius matches role (2–4 / 6 / 8px)?
- [ ] No `rounded-xl` on everyday UI?
- [ ] Border + background before shadow?
- [ ] Shadow only on overlays?

## Buttons

- [ ] One `primary` + `solid` per group?
- [ ] Cancel/secondary on `neutral` outline or ghost?
- [ ] `danger` + `solid` only on confirm?
- [ ] Icon buttons named for screen readers?
- [ ] `small` toolbars: 24px targets, 8px between neighbours?
- [ ] No solid success/warning until tokens land?

## Layout

- [ ] Aligned grid, real dividers?
- [ ] Asymmetry tied to workflow, not layout fashion?
- [ ] Geometric accents encode selection/focus/status/nav — not poster art?

## Focus and accessibility

- [ ] Visible `focus-visible` light and dark?
- [ ] `--pvc-color-focus` on new/migrated code?
- [ ] Focus distinct from accent in **both** modes?
- [ ] State not colour-only?
- [ ] Semantic HTML, AA contrast, SR names?
- [ ] `prefers-reduced-motion`?
- [ ] Forced-colours on custom controls?

## Dark mode

- [ ] No `neutral-950` page shells?
- [ ] Borders, muted text, states still clear?
- [ ] Focus not same as accent?
- [ ] Deeper black only inside framed dense regions?
- [ ] Same radius/spacing as light?

## Previews

- [ ] Realistic workflow context?
- [ ] No marketing gradients or hero layouts?
- [ ] Same tokens as shipped components?
- [ ] Checked light and dark?

## Commands

| You changed | Run |
|-------------|-----|
| CSS / tokens | `pnpm run build:css:check` |
| Ruby components | `bin/test` |
| JavaScript | `pnpm test` |
| Visible UI | Lookbook, light + dark |
